WELCOME TO CONTINENTAL CEMENT COMPANY, LLC
A wholly-owned subsidiary of Summit Materials (NYSE: SUM). We have two manufacturing facilities located in Davenport, Iowa, and Hannibal, Missouri, with distribution facilities in Des Moines, Iowa, and along the Mississippi River from Minneapolis, Minnesota, to New Orleans, Louisiana.
Our corporate office is located in Chesterfield, Missouri.
