WELCOME TO GREEN AMERICA RECYCLING

Since 1986, Green America Recycling has safely utilized waste materials to supplement coal as a fuel for the cement manufacturing process. These alternative fuels (waste materials) are an effective source of fuel that provides the needed energy to produce a quality cement product. Green America Recycling operates a Part B permitted RCRA treatment, storage, and disposal (TSD) facility adjacent to Continental Cement in Hannibal, Missouri. 
About Us










